        {
            "+content": "Toya Senji is a teenage boy struggling with low self-esteem after growing up in the shadow of his gifted older brother. He comes to the decision that academic studies are his last resort in the search for talent, but fails to find satisfaction despite constantly placing in the top 100 for national mock exams. In a twist of fate, Toya encounters one of his classmates, Haito Luo Buffett, a \"Returner\" who has resurrected the talents of her past life using the Branch of Reincarnation, as she fights against a serial killer.",
            "+@gid": "2097581860",
